    bottomLine: "Consumers Credit Union is the go-to for refinancing older vehicles. While most lenders cap at 7-10 years, Consumers accepts vehicles up to 15 years old with up to 125,000 miles. Their rates remain competitive despite the flexibility. Membership is required but open to anyone for a small fee. A hidden gem for older car owners.",
